:["セロシアインターナショナルスクール","Celosia International School","青箱國際學校","瑟罗希亚国际学校","celosia_international"],"schoolCls":["なし","N/A","無","无","없음"],"schoolYear":["高校3年生（12年生）","High School 3rd-Year (Grade 12)","高中3年級(12年級)","高中3年级（12年级）",2],"part":"dj","birthday":"976114800000","constellation":"sagittarius","height":140}}